trans-unit.resname: by starting your own team, you can attract teammates and take on challenges / challenges together.

trans-unit.target: Door je eigen team te starten, kun je teamgenoten aantrekken en samen uitdagingen / challenges aangaan.

trans-unit.resname: there is no set definition of who should be on a team, so you could be a group of students from the same study or a multidisciplinary team of students from different studies.

trans-unit.resname: post a challenge and invite students to respond and pitch their ideas and / or products!
trans-unit.source: post a challenge and invite students to respond and pitch their ideas and / or products!
trans-unit.target: plaats een challenge en nodig studenten uit om te reageren en hun ideeën en / of producten te pitchen!

trans-unit.resname: are you a creative and driven student and looking for a different kind of internship? Here we offer challenges from companies with special challenges, who are looking for a suitable solution. You as a student can participate! Pitch your innovative solution / idea for these challenges and win a unique internship where you can implement your idea. You can do this individually or with others. Looking for team players watch

Hier bieden we uitdagingen aan van bedrijven met bijzondere challenges, die op zoek zijn naar een passende oplossing. Jij als student kan meedoen! Pitch jouw innovatieve oplossing / idee voor deze uitdagingen en win een unieke stage waarin jij jouw idee kunt implementeren. U kunt dit individueel of met anderen doen. Op zoek naar teamspelers kijken

trans-unit.resname: interns are of big value, they bring new and fresh energy to your organization! Also they are the future employees :)
trans-unit.source: interns are of big value, they bring new and fresh energy to your organization! Also they are the future employees :)
trans-unit.target: Stagiaires zijn van grote waarde, ze brengen nieuwe en frisse energie in uw organisatie! Zij zijn ook de toekomstige werknemers :)

trans-unit.resname: they say 1+1=3, so that’s why we recommend students to work in teams on challenges! Together you can come up with the best solutions for challenges.
trans-unit.source: they say 1+1=3, so that’s why we recommend students to work in teams on challenges! Together you can come up with the best solutions for challenges.
trans-unit.target: Ze zeggen 1 + 1 = 3, dus daarom raden we studenten aan om in teams aan uitdagingen te werken! Samen bedenk je de beste oplossingen voor uitdagingen.

trans-unit.resname: We collect as many tutorials as possible that share your knowledge and which increases the chance of a great internship! For some internships it is going through a few tutorials is a must, you will then submit a little after watching test so that the company can see that you have acquired the knowledge. That also makes it much easier for you to immediately join your internship company

Dat maakt het voor jou ook veel gemakkelijker om direct bij je stagebedrijf te komen

trans-unit.resname: interns can help us to solve challenges we experience inside or outside our organizations. they have a fresh and new perspective on things. Let/s focus on what interns need to learn to transform their fresh brain to strategic problem-solving skills. so instead of offering a student an internship, provide them with a challenge to solve.
trans-unit.source: interns can help us to solve challenges we experience inside or outside our organizations. they have a fresh and new perspective on things. Let/s focus on what interns need to learn to transform their fresh brain to strategic problem-solving skills. so instead of offering a student an internship, provide them with a challenge to solve.
trans-unit.target: stagiaires kunnen ons helpen bij het oplossen van challenges die we binnen of buiten onze organisaties ervaren. Ze hebben een frisse en nieuwe kijk op dingen. Laten we ons concentreren op wat stagiaires nodig hebben om te leren om hun frisse brein om te zetten in strategische probleemoplossende vaardigheden. Dus in plaats van een student een stageplaats aan te bieden, geef ze een challenge om op te lossen.
